models.name: square card reader helper (with case on I phone)
models.description:
This is a square credit card reader that makes it easy to swipe faster.  

the stick is so you can get out the square.  

the part that helps it swipe better needs to be hot glued to the case once you put in the square.
models.instructions:
1: Put your case on your I phone 5 (maybe 5 S),  

2: Put square in helper piece,  

3: Put a dab of hot glue on the extra part extruding from the bottom right part of the case,  

4: Put the helper piece with the square in it in the headphone jack on the phone in the case. Make sure to make it so the helper is touching the hot glue.  

5: To take out the square and then take out the I phone, use the wedge or use keys, paperclip,ect to take out the square and then take out the I phone normally.  

6: Take pictures  

7: upload a Make!
